CatDescriptText: Related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 6, 1961, pg. A16 reads: "D.I. Club Toasts New Members - The smart D.I. Club of Pittsburgh has added three new members to the select group, whose fashion shows annually benefit the National Foundation (for infantile paralysis). Toasting the club at a recent meeting were, left to right: Margye Allen, a new member; Doryce Griffin, President Gaye DeHall, Myna Kavaler, a new member, and Rubye Buchanan.  Another new D.I., not shown, is Stephaney Bindley.  The club plans a fascinating "thank you" party in June. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Meeting of new and established members of the D.I. Club from left to right: Margye Allen, Doryce Griffin, president Gaye DeHall standing in center, Myna Kavaler, and Ruby Buchanan, possibly in Loendi Club
